Stokesâ€™ Theorem:<br />
\(\oint_{c}\bar{F}\cdot d\bar{l}=\iint_{S}\triangledown \times \bar{F}\cdot \hat{n}dS\)<br />
<br />
Divergence Theorem:<br />
\(\oiint_{S}\bar{F}\cdot \hat{n}dS=\iiint_{V}\triangledown \cdot \bar{F}dV\)<br />
